bhuq SwsqR qy bhu isMmRiqIAW, swry (AsW) Koj ky vyKy hn; (ieh pusqk keI qrHW dI igAwn-crcw qy keI Dwrimk qy BweIcwrk rsmW isKwauNdy hn)
(pr ieh) Akwl purK dy nwm dI brwbrI nhIN kr skdy[ hy nwnk! (pRBU dy) nwm dw mu`l nhIN pwieAw jw skdw ]1]
