(jy koeI) (vyd-mMqRW dy) jwp kry, (srIr nUM DUxIAW nwl) qpwey, (hor) keI igAwn (dIAW g`lW kry) qy (dyviqAW dy) iDAwn Dry,
Cy SwsqRW qy isimRqIAW dw aupdyS kry;
jog dy swDn kry, krm kWfI Drm dI ikRAw kry,
(jW) swry (kMm) C`f ky jMglW ivc BauNdw iPry;
AnykW iksmW dy bVy jqn kry,
puMndwn kry qy bhuq swrw iGau hvn kry,
Awpxy srIr nUM rqI rqI kr ky ktwvy qy A`g ivc swV dyvy,
keI iksmW dy vrqW dy bMDyj kry;
(pr ieh swry hI) pRBU dy nwm dI ivcwr dy brwbr nhIN hn,
(BwvyN) hy nwnk! ieh nwm iek vwrI (BI) gurU dy snmuK ho ky jipAw jwey ]1]
(jy koeI mnu`K) swrI DrqI qy iPry, lMmI aumr qk jIaUNdw rhy,
(jgq vloN) bhuq auprwm ho ky v`fw qpI bx jwey;
A`g ivc (AwpxI) ijMd hvn kr dyvy;
sonw, GoVy, vDIAw GoVy qy izmIN dwn kry;
inaulI krm qy hor bhuq swry (Xog) Awsn kry,
jYnIAW dy rsqy (c`l ky) bVy kiTn swDn qy sMjm kry;
srIr nUM rqw rqw kr ky ktw dyvy,
qW BI (mn dI) haumY dI mYl dUr nhIN huMdI[
(Ajyhw) koeI (au~dm) pRBU dy nwm dy brwbr nhIN hY;
hy nwnk! jo mnu`K gurU dy snmuK ho ky nwm jpdy hn auh au~cI Awqmk AvsQw hwsl krdy hn ]2]
(keI pRwxIAW dy) mn dI ie`Cw (huMdI hY ik) qIrQW qy (jw ky) srIrk colw C`ifAw jwey,
(pr ies qrHW BI) haumY AhMkwr mn ivcoN Gtdw nhIN[
(mnu`K) idn qy rwq (Bwv, sdw) (qIrQW qy) ieSnwn kry,
(Pyr BI) mn dI mYl srIr DoiqAW nhIN jWdI[
(jy) ies srIr nUM (swDn dI ^wqr) keI jqn BI kry,
(qW BI) kdy mn qoN mwieAw (dw pRBwv) nhIN tldw[
(jy) ies nwsvMq srIr nUM keI vwr pwxI nwl BI Dovy,
(qW BI ieh srIr rUpI) k`cI kMD ikQy pivqR ho skdI hY?
hy mn! pRBU dy nwm dI vifAweI bhuq v`fI hY[
hy nwnk! nwm dI brkiq nwl Axigxq mMd-krmI jIv (ivkwrW qoN) bc jWdy hn ]3]
(jIv dI) bhuqI cqurweI (dy kwrx) jmW dw fr (jIv nUM) Aw dbWdw hY,
(ikauNik cqurweI dy) AnykW jqn kIiqAW (mwieAw dI) iqRh nhIN mu`kdI[
AnykW (Dwrimk) ByK kIiqAW (iqRSnw dI) A`g nhIN bu`JdI,
(ieho ijhy) kRoVW qrIky (vriqAW BI pRBU dI) drgwh ivc sur^rU nhIN hoeIdw[
(iehnW jqnW nwl) jIv cwhy AkwS qy cVH jwey, cwhy pqwl ivc luk jwey,
(mwieAw qoN) bc nhIN skdw, (sgoN) jIv mwieAw dy jwl ivc qy moh ivc Psdy hn[
(nwm qoN ibnw) hor swrIAW krqUqW nUM jmrwj fMn lWdw hY,
pRBU dy Bjn qoN ibnW rqw BI nhIN pqIjdw[
(jo mnu`K) hir-nwm aucwrdw hY aus dw du`K (pRBU dw nwm jpidAW) dUr ho jWdw hY)
hy nwnk! (jdoN auh) Awqmk Afolqw ivc itk ky pRym nwl (hir-nwm) aucwrdw hY ]4]
jy koeI mnu`K (Drm, ArQ, kwm, moK) cwr pdwrQW dw loVvMd hovy,
(qW aus nUM cwhIdw hY ik) gurmuKW dI syvw ivc l`gy[
jy koeI mnu`K Awpxw du`K imtwxw cwhy,
qW pRBU dw nwm sdw ihrdy ivc ismry[
jy koeI mnu`K AwpxI soBw cwhuMdw hovy hY,
qW sqsMg ivc (rih ky) ies haumY dw iqAwg kry[
jy koeI mnu`K jnm mrn (dy gyV) qoN frdw hovy,
qW auh sMqW dI crnIN l`gy[
ijs mnu`K nUM pRBU dy dIdwr dI qWG hY,
hy nwnk! (AwK ik) mYN aus qoN sdw sdky jwvW ]5]
(auh) mnu`K swry mnu`KW ivcoN v`fw hY,
sq sMg ivc (rih ky) ijs mnu`K dw AhMkwr imt jWdw hY[
jo mnu`K Awpxy Awp nUM (swirAW nwloN) mMd-krmI ^iAwl krdw hY,
aus nUM swirAW nwloN cMgw smJxw cwhIdw hY[
ijs mnu`K dw mn sBnW dy crnW dI DUV huMdw hY (Bwv, jo sB nwl grIbI-suBwau vrqdw hY)
aus mnu`K ny hryk srIr ivc pRBU dI s`qw pCwx leI hY[
ijs ny Awpxy mn ivcoN burweI imtw id`qI hY,
auh swrI isRStI (dy jIvW nUM Awpxw) imqR vyKdw hY[
(ieho ijhy) mnu`K suKW qy duKW nUM ieko ijhw smJdy hn,
hy nwnk! (qwhIeyN) pwp qy puMn dw auhnW auqy Asr nhIN huMdw (Bwv, nwh koeI mMdw krm auhnW dy mn nUM Psw skdw hY, qy nwh hI surg Awidk dw lwlc kr ky jW du`K klyS qoN fr ky auh puMn krm krdy hn, auhnW dw suBwv hI nykI krnw bx jWdw hY) ]6]
(hy pRBU) kMgwl vwsqy qyrw nwm hI Dn hY,
inAwsry nUM qyrw Awsrw hY[
inmwxy vwsqy qyrw (nwm), hy pRBU! Awdr mwx hY,
qUM swry jIvW nUM dwqW dyNdw hYN[
qUM Awp hI sB kuJ krdw hYN, qy, Awp hI krwauNdw hYN[
hy suAwmI! hy swry pRwxIAW dy idl dI jwxn vwly!
hy pRBU! qUM AwpxI hwlq qy AwpxI (vifAweI dI) mrXwdw Awp hI jwxdw hYN;
qUM Awpxy Awp ivc Awp hI mgn hYN[
(hy pRBU!) qyrI vifAweI qYQoN hI (ibAwn) ho skdI hY,
hy nwnk! (AwK, ik) koeI hor qyrI vifAweI nhIN jwxdw ]7]
(hy mn!) ieh Drm swry DrmW nwloN cMgw hY-
pRBU dw nwm jp (qy) pivqR Awcrx (bxw)[
